{"tid":850022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"l【逗陰】情侶買車殺到最低價！卻拿3張八萬「麻將牌」付款　遭群毆","createTime":"2018-10-06T06:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T03:59:01.000Z","uid":179810,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c5bed5511fad8e488d9c886a05a5d81b641089b6","tid":850022,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T06:49:03.000Z","msg":"大陸廣東中山一對情侶為了拍「抖音」影片，日前到汽車展示間買車，不料談了半天要了各種優惠，銷售人員要他們付款時，情侶卻拿出出來3張八萬「麻將牌」付款，讓店內銷售員全傻了，直接將兩人暴打一頓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/10/06/1576270-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F10%2F06%2F1576270-XXL.jpg&h=a136439c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲情侶買車殺到最低價！卻拿3張八萬「麻將牌」付款遭群毆。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n綜合陸媒報導，一名情侶日前到了到4S馬自達店內說要以現金買車，並與一名男業務詳談了大半天，逼得業務員好不容易從店經理那拿到超值優惠價格，不料銷售人員準備向情侶拿錢辦理一切手續時，情侶卻拿出「3張八萬的麻將牌」說要付24萬元人民幣的車款，並說「正在拍抖音」讓銷售員傻眼，直接暴打該情侶，甚至店內其他銷售員得知，也跟著追打該情侶。<br />\n<br />\n影片中可見，該情侶至少遭到7名男業務圍毆，期間女子遭推擠、摔到了地上，男子則遭緊緊抓住，遭拳頭毆打、腳踢；直到2名男子勸阻，所以人才停下動作。對此，網友看到影片後，紛紛表示「好療癒啊」、「再抖啊！欠打」、「讓人忙大班天！最後撲空該死」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JQJyuruNsPQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJQJyuruNsPQ&d=tmnNc1%2F5Cp15QOcWwSiJj4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=fd0d7425\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JQJyuruNsPQ</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你咁都打唔死"},{"pid":"df962455688ef2b43882a06d92ba62dfbd5c95fb","tid":850022,"uid":11694,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T06:51:51.000Z","msg":"On99，阻人揾食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96727bd069160830b0be238de4141788faf0c05b","tid":850022,"uid":58089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T06:54:09.000Z","msg":"成條片重複幾十次"},{"pid":"f634ac73818081d99413d764021e6c3aea07daaa","tid":850022,"uid":193709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:04:34.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebabca787b6b3adc9dadec06004f4568114cbcf","tid":850022,"uid":82845,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:06:23.000Z","msg":"都話抖陰玩撚壞腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870c6c2411b6db869670e418d312317c9db60e8a","tid":850022,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:06:42.000Z","msg":"拍抖音係咪就係拍佢地俾人打"},{"pid":"21e612fc8a98b9af0f808a99abe2a19824af4199","tid":850022,"uid":54930,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:06:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">IT IS JUST A PRANK</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec27ed100b29e7bdf8478188ae7f64d69c6df6d4","tid":850022,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:14:16.000Z","msg":"打唔死已經好好彩 <br />\n要佢吞埋果三舊八萬先比佢走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713f56d4b434e7864ed28051a6c55343b7e3d10a","tid":850022,"uid":96743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:19:44.000Z","msg":"咁樣打人係唔岩架<br />\n應該男既摘器官 女既推火坑<br />\n比佢地邊摘器官/邊接客個陣拍抖音拍爆佢"},{"pid":"bcbf3d205155b877cb53a8e032778d6676564d09","tid":850022,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T09:32:18.000Z","msg":"It&rsquo;s funny <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c04098e395bb17d6f5731039ae4196a987976d","tid":850022,"uid":37516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T09:42:42.000Z","msg":"諗住張圖"},{"pid":"37dd472693bd063482a83d88be98eb7f7f388b14","tid":850022,"uid":17368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T03:56:29.000Z","msg":"得罪方丈仲想走？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d572ab08247c1b7804b3c617e402e86113e406","tid":850022,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited